text: Ohsama Sentai King-Ohger is a Japanese television series. It is the 47th Toei's Super Sentai series. Its Insectoid-themed Avataro Sentai Donbrothers The show succeeded Kamen Rider Geats and Kamen Rider Gotchard line-up Super Hero Time to Ohsama Sentai King-Ohger premiered March 5, 2023, on TV Asahi. ==Characters== ===King-Ohger=== Actor Name King-Ohger Mecha Taisei Sakai Gira Hastie Kuwagata Ohger God Kuwagata Aōto Watanabe Yanma Gust Tombo Ohger God Tombo Erica Murakami Hymeno Ran Kamakiri Ohger God Kamakiri Yuzuki Hirakawa Rita Kaniska Papillon Ohger God Papillon So Kaku Kaguraki Dybowski Hachi Ohger God Hachi Masashi Ikeda Jeremy Braseiri Spider Kumonos God Tarantula Masato Yano Racles Hastie Ōokuwagata Ohger God Kuwagata Zero ==Cast== * Gira Hastie / Kuwagata Ohger: Taisei Sakai * Yanma Gust / Tombo Ohger: Aoto Watanabe * Hymeno Ran / Kamakiri Ohger: Erica Murakami * Rita Kaniska / Papillon Ohger: Yuzuki Hirakawa * Kaguraki Dybowski / Hachi Ohger: So Kaku * Jeremy Braseiri / Spider Kumonos: Masashi Ikeda * Racles Hastie / Okuwagata Ohger: Masato Yano * Duga: Yutaka Morioka * Bocimar: Jubun Fukuzawa * Shiokara: Yuhei Chiawata * Sebastian: Hiroto Yoshimitsu * Morfonia: Kasumi Hasegawa * Kogane: Anna Hoshino * Bun: Minato Kiso * Akka: Hokuto Minami * Usuba: Kaito Okano * Mayuta: Nagisa Hayakawa ===Guest cast=== * Ian Yorkland / Kyoryu Black (32, 33): Syuusuke Saito * Noboharu Udo / Kyoryu Blue (32, 33): Yamato Kinjo * Souji Rippukan / Kyoryu Green (32, 33): Akihisa Shiono * Amy Yuzuki / Kyoryu Pink (32, 33): Ayuri Konno * Gentle (32): Kentaro Shimazu * Daigo Kiryu / Kyoryu Red (32, 33): Ryo Ryusei * Kyoryu Gold Voice (32): Atsushi Maruyama * Yoko Fukui (33): Ayumi Kinoshita * Marina Iko (38): Rina Ikoma ==Theme song== * "Zenryoku King" ("Full Power King") ** Composition & Arrangement: Kentaro Sonada ** Lyrics & Artist: Takayuki Furukawa Category:Super Sentai series
